      "text": "Triple Play 98 is a baseball sports video game which was released in 1997 on the PlayStation and Microsoft Windows. The game was developed and published by EA Sports, and the next entry in the Triple Play series after Triple Play 97. The cover of the game features St. Louis Cardinals player Brian Jordan.",
